| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0021 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fb0d4dc5-2db9-574b-b7fa-3f35183bcb0a"
